---
// Hero component
---

<header class="section__container header__container" id="inicio">
  <div class="video-container">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fast.wistia.com">
    <script src="https://fast.wistia.com/player.js" async></script>
    <script src="https://fast.wistia.com/embed/50onh39pm2.js" async type="module"></script>
    <style>
      wistia-player[media-id='50onh39pm2']:not(:defined) { 
        background: center / contain no-repeat url('https://fast.wistia.com/embed/medias/50onh39pm2/swatch'); 
        display: block; 
        filter: blur(5px); 
        padding-top:56.25%; 
      }
    </style> 
    <wistia-player media-id="50onh39pm2" aria-label="Video explicativo sobre crédito de libranza para pensionados"></wistia-player>
  </div>

  <div class="header__content">
    <div>
      <h1>Rápido, sencillo y confiable: Crédito de libranza diseñado para pensionados, maestros y policías.</h1>
    </div>
    <p class="horas">
      Aprobación en 4 horas
    </p>
    <div class="header__btn">
      <a href="https://wa.me/573505489828" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn">
        <span><i class="ri-whatsapp-line"></i></span> Asesoría Gratis
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<style>
  /* Header styles */
  .header__container {
    padding-top: 5rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .header__content {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .header__content h1 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .horas {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #00aa44;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .header__btn {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  /* Video container styles */
  .video-container {
    position: relative;
    padding-bottom: 56.25%; /* 16:9 Aspect Ratio */
    height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 100%;
    isolation: isolate;
    z-index: -1;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .video-container wistia-player {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border-radius: 1rem;
  }

  /* Desktop styles */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .header__container {
      padding-top: 5rem;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      align-items: center;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .video-container {
      grid-area: 1/3/2/5;
      max-width: none;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .header__content {
      grid-area: 1/1/2/3;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .header__content h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      line-height: 3rem;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .horas {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .header__content h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .horas {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
    }
  }
</style>